data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming Cape Cod-style home is situated on a large cul-de-sac lot, offering both comfort and tranquility. With a host of recent upgrades, this home only awaits your individualized touch. The recent updates include the kitchen, thoughtfully updated with ceramic tile flooring & boasts elegant granite countertops that perfectly complement the space, new windows, a fenced yard, & a deck. Located just minutes away from the Langley Air Force Base, Buckrose Beach, & downtown Hampton. This home offers the perfect blend of peaceful living & convenience. Enjoy easy access to key destinations while returning to your serene haven at the end of the day.  ****Seller's Home Warranty to Transfer to Buyer***
